{"type": "article", "id": 28590, "title": "拥有独特防盗功能的自行车", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-23T06:51:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154942GjTZhYCc0tUB9zmH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>设计师 Jens Martin Skibsted 最近推出了一款极具创意的自行车 Biomega BOS 8，采用大号的金属管材和结实的轮胎来处理各种路面环境。它有着一套独特的防盗系统：自行车的框架中有一条特殊的钢丝车锁，被剪断后车架就会断裂，这样一来整部自行车都无法继续使用。和需要经常润滑的链条传动方式不同，BOS 8 利用的是皮带传动，不仅结实也免去了噪音，骑行时也不需要靠边调整链条。全铝合金框架看起来干练时尚，全车重量仅有 15.3 千克，便于携带。这是它的<a href=\"https://biomega.com/product/bos-8-speed-basket/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1199 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154939gCTthmA5KpxUrl6J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154940tPMZ3JdmV92wzHLR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154941EqXUdi0Qhgsea67u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154941tVhJpLevUSOPcN5x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}